THIRD-PARTY NOTICES

This plugin builds on the Detexify project by Daniel Kirsch, which is also
distributed under the MIT License (Copyright (c) 2009 Daniel Kirsch).

  - The stroke-preprocessing and nearest-neighbour (DTW) classifier in
    src/classifier.ts is a TypeScript port of the Detexify classifier.
        https://github.com/kirel/detexify

  - The bundled training data in data/snapshot.json and the symbol metadata in
    data/symbols.json are derived from the Detexify data set (filtered to the
    symbols Obsidian's MathJax can render and re-serialised by
    scripts/build-data.cjs).
        https://github.com/kirel/detexify-hs-backend

